      <updated>2018-04-12T00:00:00+01:00</updated>
      <id>http://www.bnlawrence.net//management/2018/04/workload</id>
      <content type="html" xml:base="http://www.bnlawrence.net//management/2018/04/workload/">&lt;p&gt;I’ve always wondered where I spend my time. I keep records for some projects because one has to, but I’ve never found a way of recording interesting information easily enough. That changed recently: it turns out it is now possible to get a handle on where you spend time pretty easily, and at the same time learn about what applications you use most.&lt;/p&gt;</content>

      
      
      
      
      

